<td><strong>Active directory synchronization</strong></td>
<td><strong>Yes.</strong> ADSync software allows for easy sharing of Active Directory attributes with Live-Tech hosted Exchange and Single Sign-On.</td>
<td><strong>Limited.</strong> Google Apps Directory Sync is LDAP only and does not allow Single Sign-On.</td>
