<td><strong>Yes.</strong> Schedule shared resources like meeting rooms, conference lines or projectors via Outlook or OWA.</td>
<td><strong>Limited. </strong>Resource mailboxes are only available in the cloud, not via Google Sync for Outlook.</td>
