<td><a title="Our Data Center" href="http://www.livetechexchange.com/our-data-center/" target="_blank">Live-Tech's Canadian data centers</a> use a <strong>renewable energy</strong> source, hydro-electricity, making our data centers <span style="color: #008000;"><strong>100% Green.</strong></span></td>
